    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.6">
<l>uṇarntuṇarn tiḻintakaṉ ṟuyarnturu viyantavinnilaimai</l>
<l>yuṇarntuṇarn tuṇarilum iṟainilaiyuṇarvari tuyirkā</l>
<l>ḷuṇarntuṇarn turaitturait tariyaya ṉaraṉeṉṉumivarai</l>
<l>yuṇarntuṇarn turaitturait tiṟaiñcumiṉ maṉappaṭṭatoṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Perceiving, perceiving, falling, departing, rising, wondering at the form, even though</l>
<l>perceiving, perceiving, perceiving the this wonderful state, perceiving the state of the lord is difficult to perceive, oh living beings.</l>
<l>Perceiving, perceiving, talking, talking about him called Hari, Aja [and] Hara</l>
<l>perceiving, perceiving, talking, talking bow, agreeing as one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
